  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.58,
      515.9,
      535.73,
      555.65
    ],
    "text": "Fairly heavy falls above 50 mm are likely at some places in Sabaragamuwa, Central and North-central provinces and in Badulla district.",
