      558.95,
      538.61,
      596.21
    ],
    "text": "Showers are likely in coastal areas of Southern province and in Kalutara and Colombo districts during the morning too.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
